files.name: .gitpod.yml
files.content:
ports:
    - port: 8000
      onOpen: open-preview
tasks:
    - init: >
        npm install &&
        cd site && npm install;
      command: >
        cd site && npm run start;

files.name: .mergify.yml
files.content:
pull_request_rules:
  - name: automatic merge when GitHub branch protection passes on master
    conditions:
      - base=master
    actions:
      merge:
        method: merge
